slayzone_shell_ui: chrome://slayzone-shell/ host. SimpleURLLoader server-side
proxy to Vite dev server in dev mode (preserves chrome:// origin so Mojo
bindings work). CSP widened in dev for inline scripts + ws://localhost HMR.
slayzone_shell_container: replaces 14-region grid with full-bleed shell
WebView in browser_view.
Registry registers SlayzoneShellUI alongside existing per-region hosts.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
